pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.utilities

Class DataProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • pme.ai.fhe.de.studybuddy.utilities.DataProvider

  • public class DataProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides all the data necessary for creating the database. Since the async task can not handle ArrayLists, all the data is generated with normal arrays.
